Package: ADS8192
Title: ADS 8192 Gene Correlation Network Tool
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Liane", "Muir", email = "liane.muir@stjude.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Provides functions to build and analyze gene co-expression networks
    from bulk RNA-seq data. Includes tools for selecting the most variable genes,
    computing pairwise gene-gene correlation matrices, and thresholding correlations
    into binary adjacency matrices with per-gene (node-level) statistics.
    Supports community detection using Louvain or walktrap algorithms with
    per-module summaries and global network statistics. Provides visualizations as
    correlation heatmaps or force-directed layouts colored by module with hub gene
    labels. Exports results to TSV files.
